<bibRefCitation author="Thomas" box="[542,694,1016,1039]" firstAuthor="Thomas" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" pagination="1 - 12" refId="ref27909" refString="Thomas, R. (1965) The genus Leptotyphlops in the West Indies with the description of a new species from Hispaniola (Serpentes, Leptotyphlopidae). Breviora, Museum of Comparative Zoology, 1 - 12." type="book chapter" year="1965">Thomas, 1965</bibRefCitation>
